    "name": "Legends of the Round Table",
    "steam_appid": 2387040,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/6412c25387adde75f2bb5cb1f7f4edee.avif?t=1771956873\" width=1170 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/a6f071beaf8b0f0e219b33df7f205d2f.avif?t=1771956873\" width=1170 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/9cce75d31fb1a85da5f15d307b1d4c51.poster.avif?t=1771956873\" width=800 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/9cce75d31fb1a85da5f15d307b1d4c51.webm?t=1771956873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/9cce75d31fb1a85da5f15d307b1d4c51.mp4?t=1771956873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Legends of the Round Table》里了解中世纪骑士的真正含义。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这一款充满荣誉、魔法以及浪漫元素的真实中世纪角色扮演游戏中，带领圆桌骑士们穿越亚瑟王传奇！踏上源自真实中世纪故事的冒险之旅，伴随着精心绘制的美丽艺术，采用正宗的饰边手稿技术，以及源自13世纪实际作曲和诗歌的音乐配乐，运用真实的、符合时代的乐器演奏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/ce6da2af15cf86a70f98d093c137005a.avif?t=1771956873\" width=1170 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/6f290880dbf5d525795afccd5b28fefd.poster.avif?t=1771956873\" width=800 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/6f290880dbf5d525795afccd5b28fefd.webm?t=1771956873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/6f290880dbf5d525795afccd5b28fefd.mp4?t=1771956873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的视觉效果灵感源自于13世纪的饰边手稿，游戏环境由中世纪专家采用真实的中世纪绘画技法手绘而成，忠实再现了当时可用的工具、染料和色彩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/1821e6fd2b6a1d5391b97c1bc79253b2.avif?t=1771956873\" width=1170 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/9d9f1e3afe6a32e7f55bb07b69263a6d.poster.avif?t=1771956873\" width=800 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/9d9f1e3afe6a32e7f55bb07b69263a6d.webm?t=1771956873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/9d9f1e3afe6a32e7f55bb07b69263a6d.mp4?t=1771956873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每次冒险中，玩家会遇到阴谋、神秘、爱情和冲突。玩家所做的每一个决定，比如对待战败的对手给予宽恕、判处罪犯死刑，甚至沉迷于浪漫，都会影响您的荣誉以及您所在国家的未来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/46c6414c19c47686b122cb0214fac5f6.avif?t=1771956873\" width=1170 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/39077d49a204a9956b9a80d7b807d36a.poster.avif?t=1771956873\" width=800 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/39077d49a204a9956b9a80d7b807d36a.webm?t=1771956873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/39077d49a204a9956b9a80d7b807d36a.mp4?t=1771956873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >骑枪冲锋、侍从交换武器并俘虏敌人以索取赎金、光荣的决斗和致命的遭遇是我们策略性、回合制战斗系统的支柱。每一场战斗都很重要，失败是永恒的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/718a21cac3a70f72c8609f2c5ab70c1b.avif?t=1771956873\" width=1170 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/d942f472dd054ce81056a5e92e037b54.poster.avif?t=1771956873\" width=800 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/d942f472dd054ce81056a5e92e037b54.webm?t=1771956873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/d942f472dd054ce81056a5e92e037b54.mp4?t=1771956873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏音乐运用中世纪乐器演奏：鲁特琴、竖琴、维奥尔琴等等。每次冒险都由Boston Camerata古乐团的著名歌手Anne Azéma演绎，为游戏增添了美妙动人的歌曲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/2996222b5986457b532f31288224143f.avif?t=1771956873\" width=1170 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/f54445d33e806e3c6d59f4ba1e9f5170.poster.avif?t=1771956873\" width=800 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/f54445d33e806e3c6d59f4ba1e9f5170.webm?t=1771956873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/f54445d33e806e3c6d59f4ba1e9f5170.mp4?t=1771956873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理亚瑟王的骑士团，包括兰斯洛特爵士、高文爵士、珀西瓦里爵士等十几位骑士！选择配得上圆桌会议席位的人选，为每个任务指派最适合的骑士，监督他们的职责，并见证他们每个人的成长历程，包括成长、冲突以及最终的生命终结。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位骑士都独具特色，拥有丰富多样的发展特质，影响着他们应对挑战的方式。他们每一个都拥有自己的欲望、优势、劣势和社交偏好。并非每位骑士都能和其他人相处融洽，团队的凝聚力对他们的成功至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/a1ac0b118bffc3096450cf2aee4f28f6.avif?t=1771956873\" width=1170 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/784066dd2f98dccee6e25d37bca0010e.poster.avif?t=1771956873\" width=800 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/784066dd2f98dccee6e25d37bca0010e.webm?t=1771956873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2387040/extras/784066dd2f98dccee6e25d37bca0010e.mp4?t=1771956873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡牌系统让玩家成为自己命运的艺术家。您是选择现在就使用圣杯卡牌释放强大的法术来扭转局势，还是留到之后时机更加合适的时刻？</p>",
